19
00:00:18,356 --> 00:00:20,358
<i>Sinister forces on the move.</i>

20
00:00:20,441 --> 00:00:23,236
<i>Asajj Ventress has suffered
a humiliating betrayal</i>

21
00:00:23,277 --> 00:00:26,739
<i>at the hands of her own assassin,
Savage Opress.</i>

22
00:00:27,114 --> 00:00:28,616
<i>Having gone into hiding,</i>

23
00:00:28,699 --> 00:00:31,369
<i>she now has no choice
but to seek sanctuary</i>

24
00:00:31,452 --> 00:00:33,621
<i>with the Night sisters of Dathomir.</i>

25
00:01:16,872 --> 00:01:20,626
Sister, I knew you'd return.

26
00:01:22,837 --> 00:01:26,257
I've been hiding. Reevaluating.

27
00:01:27,008 --> 00:01:29,427
I suspected as much.

28
00:01:29,844 --> 00:01:33,848
Savage, that monster we created,
has forsaken us.

29
00:01:33,931 --> 00:01:37,518
He refused my guidance
and escaped into the galaxy.

30
00:01:38,102 --> 00:01:39,854
I have nothing.

31
00:01:40,354 --> 00:01:45,985
You have your breath, your skill,
and your sisters.

32
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:49,655
You have everything needed to survive.

33
00:01:50,114 --> 00:01:56,078
You must give up the ways of the Sith
and return to our fold.

34
00:01:56,495 --> 00:02:02,460
You will leave Dooku's absurd war behind
and remain with us.

35
00:02:02,918 --> 00:02:06,213
No longer to be ordered about.

36
00:02:06,547 --> 00:02:11,385
You will be loyal to no one but your sisters,

37
00:02:11,552 --> 00:02:13,888
and yourself.

38
00:02:14,513 --> 00:02:16,057
And then?

39
00:02:16,682 --> 00:02:20,227
And then, you will fulfill your destiny

40
00:02:20,603 --> 00:02:23,606
and become a true Night sister.

41
00:02:41,749 --> 00:02:44,126
You summoned me, My Lord?

42
00:02:44,835 --> 00:02:47,421
The time has come at last to take revenge

43
00:02:47,505 --> 00:02:51,300
on Asajj Ventress
and the witch, Mother Talzin.

44
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:55,012
I have learned Ventress
has returned to Dathomir.

45
00:02:55,596 --> 00:02:58,808
Go there and wipe the witches out.

46
00:02:59,141 --> 00:03:01,102
All of them.

47
00:03:01,227 --> 00:03:03,562
Their illusions do not frighten me.

48
00:03:03,938 --> 00:03:05,731
Yes, Master.

49
00:03:14,115 --> 00:03:16,117
Assemble the fleets.

50
00:03:16,158 --> 00:03:21,789
The time to exact vengeance against
the traitor, Ventress, has arrived.

51
00:03:22,832 --> 00:03:26,335
We go to Dathomir to battle.

52
00:03:54,613 --> 00:03:59,034
Do you pledge yourself to the sisterhood,

53
00:03:59,118 --> 00:04:03,414
to the magics, and the old ways?

54
00:04:04,623 --> 00:04:05,750
I do.

55
00:04:06,667 --> 00:04:12,339
Do you abandon
your old life for this new one?

56
00:04:12,673 --> 00:04:13,799
I do.

57
00:04:14,091 --> 00:04:18,512
Your loyalty? Your life?

58
00:04:18,596 --> 00:04:21,348
My loyalty. My life.

59
00:04:55,508 --> 00:05:01,388
You are now reborn a Sister of the Night.

60
00:05:01,764 --> 00:05:03,349
Welcome.

61
00:05:04,058 --> 00:05:05,643
Thank you, Mother.

62
00:05:06,018 --> 00:05:10,439
And now, we feast and celebrate

63
00:05:10,523 --> 00:05:13,818
the baptism of our new sister.

64
00:05:21,575 --> 00:05:24,036
We are now approaching Dathomir.

65
00:05:24,161 --> 00:05:26,705
Begin landing our troops.

66
00:05:40,719 --> 00:05:43,722
I am privileged to be your sister.

67
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:46,016
Thank you, Karis.

68
00:05:52,773 --> 00:05:54,275
Droid fighters. Scatter!

69
00:06:00,114 --> 00:06:02,783
Prepare yourselves, sisters!

70
00:06:02,867 --> 00:06:05,452
The war has come to Dathomir.

71
00:06:16,964 --> 00:06:21,051
Establish a perimeter and get the droids
in attack formation.

72
00:06:21,135 --> 00:06:25,806
We'll burn a path through the forest
right to their fortress.

73
00:07:01,592 --> 00:07:03,677
Gather your weapons!

74
00:07:04,386 --> 00:07:07,264
The droid army is only here because of me.

75
00:07:07,723 --> 00:07:10,017
And so many are going to die.

76
00:07:10,225 --> 00:07:12,603
There is no time for regret.

77
00:07:12,728 --> 00:07:14,939
Now we must fight.

78
00:07:16,023 --> 00:07:19,360
That gutless coward, Grievous,
is coordinating the attack.

79
00:07:19,443 --> 00:07:20,778
I can sense it.

80
00:07:22,154 --> 00:07:26,158
You know the droids.
It gives us an advantage.

81
00:07:37,878 --> 00:07:39,046
Karis!

82
00:07:46,011 --> 00:07:49,640
Go and lead us to victory.

83
00:08:19,211 --> 00:08:21,755
We will need an army
to fight Grievous.

84
00:08:21,797 --> 00:08:24,508
I will speak with Old Daka.

85
00:08:24,591 --> 00:08:28,012
She will get us
the reinforcements we need.

86
00:08:28,679 --> 00:08:31,598
Follow me, sisters. Attack!

87
00:08:41,942 --> 00:08:43,777
Take to the trees, sisters.

88
00:08:43,819 --> 00:08:46,989
We shall attack the droids
from above and below.

89
00:09:24,234 --> 00:09:27,321
Sir, there is heavy fighting
along the eastern front.

90
00:09:27,404 --> 00:09:30,449
Reports indicate Ventress is
leading the attack.

91
00:09:30,657 --> 00:09:33,160
Send in the Defoliator tank.

92
00:09:33,202 --> 00:09:36,789
We'll burn those witches to the ground.

93
00:09:47,508 --> 00:09:49,051
Go to my chamber.

94
00:09:49,134 --> 00:09:52,513
There you will find a small metallic sphere.

95
00:09:52,846 --> 00:09:55,140
Bring it to the hidden cave.

96
00:09:55,182 --> 00:09:57,017
Yes, Mother.

97
00:10:24,503 --> 00:10:28,882
Daka, as the oldest and wisest of us,

98
00:10:29,091 --> 00:10:32,886
I need you to resurrect our fallen sisters.

99
00:10:33,137 --> 00:10:38,392
Ventress will need the aid
of the undead army to achieve victory.

100
00:10:39,393 --> 00:10:43,730
Then I will begin the chant of resurrection.

101
00:11:27,858 --> 00:11:29,109
Rise.

102
00:11:29,860 --> 00:11:33,113
Rise. Awake, dead sisters.

103
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,740
Rise.

104
00:11:35,282 --> 00:11:37,951
Rise. Rise.

105
00:11:37,993 --> 00:11:42,539
Awake, dead sisters. Rise.

106
00:12:25,332 --> 00:12:27,167
Fire the Defoliator.

107
00:12:27,209 --> 00:12:28,377
Roger, roger.

108
00:12:57,531 --> 00:13:00,701
The army of the dead, her reinforcements.

109
00:13:32,065 --> 00:13:35,193
The undead will clear us a path
right to Grievous.

110
00:13:35,610 --> 00:13:38,947
Ventress has her army now.

111
00:13:39,281 --> 00:13:40,282
Good.

112
00:13:40,741 --> 00:13:45,579
Now I can deal with Count Dooku.

113
00:13:48,749 --> 00:13:50,500
We found it, Mother.

114
00:13:50,584 --> 00:13:53,670
Here is the orb you requested.

115
00:13:54,421 --> 00:13:56,256
Well done.

116
00:14:01,970 --> 00:14:05,515
Ah, here it is.

117
00:14:05,599 --> 00:14:11,104
A single lock of Count Dooku's silver hair.

118
00:14:11,938 --> 00:14:17,361
He should be more careful
than making deals with witches.

119
00:14:26,578 --> 00:14:29,331
Now for Dooku.

120
00:15:00,487 --> 00:15:02,364
Mother Talzin.

121
00:15:36,857 --> 00:15:38,358
Surprised?

122
00:15:39,192 --> 00:15:43,196
Hardly. You're the one I was sent here for.

123
00:15:43,530 --> 00:15:45,323
Then fight me alone.

124
00:15:45,365 --> 00:15:47,576
Prove you're the greater warrior.

125
00:15:47,701 --> 00:15:50,537
If I win, your army leaves.

126
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:54,708
If you win,
the Night sisters will surrender to you.

127
00:15:54,958 --> 00:15:57,711
I have always been greater than you.

128
00:16:07,596 --> 00:16:10,265
Pain, Count Dooku.

129
00:16:13,935 --> 00:16:17,939
You will know terrible pain.

130
00:16:27,324 --> 00:16:28,325
Enough of this.

131
00:16:33,747 --> 00:16:37,250
You think you can defeat me?
You're nothing.

132
00:16:46,468 --> 00:16:47,469
Kill her.

133
00:17:15,205 --> 00:17:18,667
Doom is upon us, sister. Run.

134
00:17:19,793 --> 00:17:21,086
Save yourself.

135
00:17:45,610 --> 00:17:50,949
Grievous, you must stop Mother Talzin
before she kills me.

136
00:17:51,366 --> 00:17:53,535
Follow the witch's magic.

137
00:17:53,618 --> 00:17:57,581
It appears as a green mist.
Follow it to its source.

138
00:17:57,664 --> 00:18:00,000
And eliminate Talzin. Quickly!

139
00:18:14,598 --> 00:18:18,893
Forget Ventress!
Our new target is Mother Talzin.

140
00:18:19,019 --> 00:18:20,687
Follow me.

141
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:33,158
Call off your army
and leave Dathomir at once.

142
00:18:33,617 --> 00:18:37,787
And let you and that traitor

143
00:18:37,871 --> 00:18:40,248
continue plotting against me?

144
00:18:40,332 --> 00:18:41,541
Never!

145
00:18:42,208 --> 00:18:46,546
You're going to die either way.

146
00:18:46,588 --> 00:18:50,717
It's only a matter of how painful it will be.

147
00:19:40,767 --> 00:19:41,893
Fire!

148
00:19:51,903 --> 00:19:53,822
No! General!

149
00:21:00,096 --> 00:21:02,891
It is over, sister.

150
00:21:03,767 --> 00:21:05,810
No one remains?

151
00:21:06,686 --> 00:21:09,439
This is all my fault.

152
00:21:10,565 --> 00:21:14,152
Where do I go? What do I do?

153
00:21:14,736 --> 00:21:18,031
This chapter is over.

154
00:21:18,114 --> 00:21:23,703
Your destiny will always
be linked with ours.

155
00:21:23,787 --> 00:21:28,958
But you have your own path to follow now.

156
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:33,671
No! Wait!

157
00:21:34,339 --> 00:21:36,424
You can't leave me here!

158
00:21:36,448 --> 00:21:41,448
http://hiqve.com/

